Atletico Madrid have replaced stars like Sergio Aguero and Diego Costa at the club . 
  Diego Simeone has been in charge of the La Liga side since 2008 . 
  Atletico have used the third party ownership loophole to their advantage . 
  Sergio Asenjo became David De Gea and Thibaut Courtois became Jan Oblak . 
  Radamel Falcao was replaced by Mario Mandzukic at Atletico Madrid . 
  Jorge Mendes has worked with the club for the last five years . 
  The club know how to replace stars with the right players . 
 